            "script": "\ttry:\n\t\tself.getChild(\"Button\").position.display \u003d True\n\t\tself.getChild(\"Button\").position.display \u003d True\n\t\tmodels, mfgList \u003d utils.deviceProfileDropDown.getDeviceProfiles(self.session.custom.tenantID)\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\ttagProviders \u003d utils.tagPathDropdown.getTagProviders()\n\t\ttagPaths \u003d utils.normalizedTagPaths.getAllTagPaths()\n\t\t\n\t\tself.custom.models \u003d models\n\t\tself.custom.mfgs \u003d mfgList\n\t\tself.custom.tagPaths \u003d tagPaths\n\t\tself.custom.tagProviders \u003d tagProviders\n\t\tself.custom.tagProvider \u003d self.session.custom.defaultTagProvider\n\t\t\n\t\tself.custom.tenant  \u003d -1\n\t\tself.custom.useCase \u003d -1\n\t\tself.custom.selectedModelID \u003d -1\n\t\tself.custom.appID \u003d enterprise.tenant.getDefaultApp()\n\t\tself.custom.parsedFile \u003d None\n\t\tself.getChild(\"FlexContainer\").getChild(\"SensorType\").getChild(\"CoordinateContainer_manufacturer\").getChild(\"Dropdown_mfg\").props.value \u003d None\n\t\t\n\t\toptions \u003d []\n\t\timport json\n\t\ttry:\n\t\t\tapps \u003d system.sitesync.listApplications()\n\t\t\ta \u003d json.loads(apps)\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tfor tenant in a:\n\t\t\t\tj \u003d {\"label\":tenant[\u0027tenantName\u0027], \"value\": tenant[\u0027id\u0027]}\n\t\n\t\t\t\toptions.append(j)\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\texcept Exception as e:\n\t\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\"Error getting apps\" + str(e))\n\t\tself.custom.apps \u003d options\n\t\t\n\texcept Exception as e:\n\t\tsystem.perspective.print(\"Error loading models: \" + str(e))"
